description: This Match up is one of the most competitive close calls we have had to date. This match actually caused us to need to evolve our set of rules. These two wrestler put everything they have into this match and at the end of the match, one wrestler has to leave the mats out of exhaustion. This wrestler did win the tie breaker, however going forward after this match, If a wrestler is too nautious, he or she will forfeit the match and their opponent will be deemed the winner and get to do what ever he or she likes. Pace yourself boys and girls.This IS real wrestling. You will be tired, you will be exhausted, but if you can’t fight, you’re gonna get fucked. Watch these two go at it in 100% real competitive wrestling. Man vs woman, power and speed against power and speed. This match is a tie at the end and a tie breaker round must happen. Indeed this calls for a rematch in the future. For today, the winner is announce and the winner gets to do what ever she or he likes to do to the loser. The Loser is choke fucked, Spun around like a little btich and taken in every way possible.
title: Bella Rossi is Annihilated in Wrestling Match then Fucked
